Sentencas: The Ag nanoparticles attached La0.6Sr0.4Co0.3Fe0.7O3-delta (LSCF) perovskites were prepared by plasma method.
Titulo: Synthesis and properties of Ag nanoparticles attached La0.6Sr0.4Co0.3Fe0.7O3-δ

Sentencas: The Ag nanoparticles with size of several nanometers evaporated from the Ag target were coated on the surface of LSCF powders with size range from 0.2 to 3 mm.
Titulo: Synthesis and properties of Ag nanoparticles attached La0.6Sr0.4Co0.3Fe0.7O3-δ

Sentencas: The agglomeration of Ag particles annealed at 800 degrees C under inert gas of Ar and N-2 were rarely observed.
Titulo: Synthesis and properties of Ag nanoparticles attached La0.6Sr0.4Co0.3Fe0.7O3-δ

Sentencas: The physical bond between surface Ag and core LSCF is effectively strong to prevent aggregation of Ag nanoparticles at high sintering temperature relate to synthesis route of cathode for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC).
Titulo: Synthesis and properties of Ag nanoparticles attached La0.6Sr0.4Co0.3Fe0.7O3-δ

Sentencas: The fuel cell showed relatively effective electric power density at operating temperature of 650 degrees C, though the extremely low Ag concentration.
Titulo: Synthesis and properties of Ag nanoparticles attached La0.6Sr0.4Co0.3Fe0.7O3-δ
